           Chiropractor, Osteopath, Naturopath, Psychologist, Dietitian, Massage Therapist, Acupuncture
         </div>
       </li>
       <li class="flex items-center">
         <span class="text-terracottaRed-darker mr-2">•</span>
         Vision Care
       </li>
       <li class="flex items-center">
         <span class="text-terracottaRed-darker mr-2">•</span>
         Prescription Drugs
       </li>
       <li class="flex items-center">
         <span class="text-terracottaRed-darker mr-2">•</span>
         Hearing and Speech Aids
       </li>
       <li class="flex items-center">
         <span class="text-terracottaRed-darker mr-2">•</span>
         Orthopedics
       </li>
       <li class="flex items-start">
         <span class="text-terracottaRed-darker mr-2">•</span>
         <div>
           <span class="font-semibold">Dental Care:</span><br/>
