         </div>
       </li>
       <li class="flex items-start">
         <span class="text-terracottaRed-darker mr-2">•</span>
         <div>
           <span class="font-semibold">Long Term Disability:</span><br/>
           Your well-being is protected with coverage through OIAC's long-term disability plan.
         </div>
       </li>
     </ul>
   </div>

   {/* Pension Plan */}
   <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8">
     <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-wood-dark mb-6">Pension Plan Snapshot</h3>
     <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
       <p>
         OIAC has a deferred contribution pension plan where an amount of money, based on your earning, is credited to an account in your name. OIAC will match that employee contribution. The employee manages the growth of the plan.
       </p>
       <p>
         Full-time and part-time employees are eligible to join the plan upon successful completion of 1 year of continuous employment with OIAC.
       </p>
       <p>
         Member contribution level is consistent with number of years served at OIAC.
       </p>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>